<post_id>930092598547476</post_id>
<electoral-propaganda-analysis>
This Facebook post, published by Regia Nationala a Padurilor - Romsilva, showcases an educational initiative involving students planting tree seedlings.  The post's content focuses on environmental education and does not mention any political candidates or parties, nor does it advocate for or against any political viewpoint related to the parliamentary elections. The images depict students participating in a tree-planting activity, supervised by forestry professionals. The text describes the educational program's goals and the partnership between Romsilva and the school. There is no call to action related to voting or any political message.  While the post falls under the "POLITICAL" category due to Facebook's broad classification, its content is purely educational and informational, promoting environmental awareness and sustainable practices.  It does not meet the criteria for electoral propaganda as defined by Article 36 (7) of LEGE nr. 334 din 17 iulie 2006.  The post does not directly refer to any candidate or party, lacks an electoral objective, and remains within the boundaries of journalistic reporting on an educational event.
</electoral-propaganda-analysis>
<electoral-propaganda-decision>FALSE</electoral-propaganda-decision>
